The paper deals with a system that involves mobile devices communicating with each other and with a server, which suggests it falls under the category of computer networks (cs.NI). The focus of the paper is on video streaming, which suggests it could also fall under multimedia (cs.MM). The paper proposes a cooperative system that involves distributed optimization, which suggests it could also fall under distributed computing (cs.DC) and systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper uses network coding, which suggests it could also fall under information theory (cs.IT).
